A simple Nepali calendar. Explore future, present and past Nepali dates, events, and even tithis with this sleek browser extension.

What's new in v 1.2.1?
You can now use and set keyboard shortcuts to open the extension and navigate around the calendar more easily. Some of them are set by default. Set/Change the keyboard shortcuts at chrome://extensions/shortcuts.
